{"tid":56620,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[自護公國殖民地] 人類需要變革","createTime":"2016-12-27T11:21:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-10T03:42:06.000Z","uid":61150,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c35c5ac80f7b5d9fd003bde16f48f3ba8165a5f8","tid":56620,"uid":61150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:21:10.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQbsjLT3fBjXWyV82P5akcYFoYhsC4M7SAgYJRtCcJXUn?filename=n349NSo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn349NSo.jpg&h=2e246fc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我們失去了一位英雄！但這意味著失敗嗎？不！這只是開始！<br />\n<br />\n和地球聯邦相比，我們自護的國力只有其三十分之一以下；儘管 有如此大的差距，我們為什麼還能戰鬥到今天呢？各位！那是因為，我們自護公國戰爭的目的是 正義的！<br />\n<br />\n由少數精英所支 配的地球聯邦，將勢力擴張到宇宙之中，統治我們長達五十餘年。居於宇宙的我們不斷要求自由，可聯邦卻多少次地將我們踐踏。在這場自護公國奮起反抗、為每一名人類的自由而戰的戰爭中，神是絕對不會將我們捨棄的！<br />\n<br />\n我的弟弟，各位所愛的卡爾瑪&middot;扎比死了！ 為什麼？<br />\n<br />\n戰局目前稍微平靜了一些；但是，面對著這場戰爭的各位，難道不是一直在以事不關己的態度遠遠旁觀嗎？這是多 麼嚴重的錯誤啊。地球聯邦污染了這神聖而不 可替代的地球，打算就此存活下去；我們必須讓地球聯邦的那些精英們為他們的愚蠢付出代價！<br />\n<br />\n而 卡爾瑪，正是為了讓各位從那種天真的夢想中醒來才死的！現在，戰爭才剛剛開始！<br />\n<br />\n我們的軍事力量正在逐漸恢復；地球聯 邦軍從此已不足為懼。<br />\n<br />\n各位的父親和兄弟，也在聯邦那無謀的抵抗中戰死。決不能忘記這悲傷和憤怒！這是卡爾瑪用自己的 死給予我們的啟示！我們現在正應集合這股怒火，消滅聯邦 軍，第一次贏得真正的勝利！這勝利，才是對戰死者最大的慰藉！<br />\n<br />\n國 民們，奮起吧！化悲痛為力量，奮起吧，國民！自護需要你們的力量！<br />\n<br />\nZick！Zeon！Zick！Zeon！</div>"},{"pid":"b9e546e9b477b562acc149e373a5f30db0446b9c","tid":56620,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:25:04.000Z","msg":"Funson<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d4568aa657027baac227520d06dec69d8ca179","tid":56620,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:25:28.000Z","msg":"Sieg Zeon Sieg Zeon Sieg Zeon Sieg Zeon Sieg Zeon Sieg Zeon"},{"pid":"f6ff5a8e707263a427e42328d4153ec19e29e843","tid":56620,"uid":61150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:26:06.000Z","msg":"我們歡迎有志之士  但絕不容忍地球聯邦的抹黑"},{"pid":"9680c5a18e8a459db0216ad6c75e8af27d24a552","tid":56620,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:27:53.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"b783698a88eed4be2af28415942ead14d492668a","tid":56620,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:05:57.000Z","msg":"聯邦爪牙無處不在"},{"pid":"187259f4ab5097bef8f3a889e6f7e6383f2b1ee7","tid":56620,"uid":30847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:27:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/"},{"pid":"7da8e3346b6db7d2ba9cbcd31b57a6d7ac314eca","tid":56620,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/27/202927_1edf583b24b174409284027d1cac9c00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F27%2F202927_1edf583b24b174409284027d1cac9c00.jpg&h=1b10cb6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24937fe08622a18eda117b2f8224b984dfc1c77b","tid":56620,"uid":61150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:30:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/27/202927_1edf583b24b174409284027d1cac9c00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F27%2F202927_1edf583b24b174409284027d1cac9c00.jpg&h=1b10cb6c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n聖光啊..."},{"pid":"aa7c528599267c8c77219801a8e97987eac98db1","tid":56620,"uid":7165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T14:14:02.000Z","msg":"自護萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a72eb6fd493350900401b3d22b0515e721e0aa","tid":56620,"uid":61150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:51:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自護萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><b